### 获取食物字典列表
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/fooddicts/fooddicts
Content-Type: application/json

### 添加食物字典
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/fooddicts/fooddict
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "id": 0,
    "class_id": 0,
    "name": "白菜",
    "image": "",
    "description": "这种蔬菜富含维生素C和维生素A，对护眼有好处，也可以帮助降低血脂。",
}

### 获取所有食物分类
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/fooddicts/allfoodclass
Content-Type: application/json


### 添加食物分类
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/fooddicts/foodclass
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "id": 0,
    "name": "蔬菜"
}
